        "edbb": {
          "role": "multipurpose",
          "intro": "A balanced cheap multirole fit. Initial is buy-only; A-rated is the multirole baseline; Engineered makes it a sharp little do-everything ship, ready to re-tune.",
          "callout": {
            "label": "A little of everything",
            "text": "One balanced fit; the Cobra re-tunes easily — add a fuel scoop and SRV to explore, fill with cargo to trade, or load all guns for combat. It does none to the top, but all of it well enough, and lands anywhere for next to nothing."
          },
          "notes": {
            "MediumHardpoint1": "Main gimballed multi-cannon; Overcharged for DPS, Corrosive Shell strips target resistance for the whole battery.",
            "MediumHardpoint2": "Gimballed pulse for shield-stripping; Efficient keeps it power-cheap, Thermal Vent vents heat on a small hull.",
            "SmallHardpoint1": "Second multi-cannon; Overcharged with Auto Loader so it never stops firing.",
            "SmallHardpoint2": "Small pulse adds chip damage; Efficient + Thermal Vent run it cold.",
            "TinyHardpoint1": "Single Heavy-Duty booster multiplies the bi-weave's raw MJ — the cheapest large gain in shield strength.",
            "TinyHardpoint2": "Optional / low-priority — Ammo Capacity adds heat-sink charges. Dumps heat for silent running and Thermal-Vent resets.",
            "PowerPlant": "A-rated size-4 plant powers guns, shield and cell; Overcharged adds headroom, Thermal Spread bleeds the extra heat.",
            "MainEngines": "A-rated thrusters + Dirty Drives give the Cobra its signature pace.",
            "FrameShiftDrive": "A-rated + Increased Range with Mass Manager for travel and respectable exploration jumps.",
            "LifeSupport": "D-rate to save mass; Lightweight trims more — life support has no experimental effect.",
            "PowerDistributor": "A-rate for weapon and boost regen; Engine Focused biases capacity toward the drives.",
            "Radar": "D-rate and go Lightweight; a multirole Cobra needs no sensor range, so save the mass.",
            "FuelTank": "Stock C tank; fuel capacity is fixed and cannot be engineered.",
            "Slot01_Size4": "Bi-weave regenerates fast under fire; Reinforced maximises MJ and Hi-Cap adds capacity.",
            "Slot02_Size4": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot03_Size4": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot04_Size2": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo.",
            "Slot05_Size2": "Optional / low-priority — Specialised cuts the cell bank's heat and power spike. Burst shield healing for emergencies.",
            "Slot06_Size2": "Hull Reinforcement adds effective armour; Heavy Duty + Deep Plating is the cheapest big gain.",
            "Slot07_Size1": "Optional / low-priority — Expanded Probe Scanning widens probe coverage. Maps planets for exploration data.",
            "Slot08_Size1": "Optional — Expanded Capacity adds cargo space; worth it for dedicated haulers. Holds cargo."
